snippet.title: Know the Stiff RBI Guidelines on Cash Payment for Marriage Expenses

localized.description:
Know the stiff RBI guidelines on cash payment for marriage expenses. Modi government has announced that families indulge in marriages can withdraw upto Rs 2.5 lakhs from banks.
